  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0baa\u0baf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "President Gotabaya left Maldives for Singapore",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and his counterpart Ayoma Rajapaksa and two security officers were to board a Singapore Airlines flight to Singapore.",
        "In this case, President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and his entourage left for Singapore today from Velana International Airport in Maldives on a Saudi Airlines flight.",
        "The protest that took place in the capital on the 9th intensified to urge President Gotabaya Rajapaksa to step down.",
        "Following the siege of the Presidential Palace, the security forces, including the president and his close associates, were kept in a safe place by the security forces.",
        "Later, President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and the important parties including his Pariyar were sent to the Maldives in the Air Force's own military plane from Katunayake Bandaranaike International Airport at 1.45 am last Wednesday.",
        "It is said that the President and his delegation reached Mal\u00e9, the capital of the Maldives, around 3 am that day.",
        "Sri Lankans living in Maldives protested near Carnival Park in Maldives on Wednesday 13th, insisting that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and his party should not be given asylum or temporary shelter in Maldives.",
        "It is noteworthy that thousands of people have tracked President Gotabaya Rajapaksa's SV788 flight from Maldives to Singapore through the app."
      ],
